        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=Email Content:\n\n\nName (if the name is not present in mail use this name): {{ $json.from.value[0].name }}\n\nSubject: {{$json.subject}}\n\nFrom: {{ $json.from.value[0].address }}\n\nBody:\n{{$json.text}}\n\nYou will receive an email. Extract the required fields and return ONLY valid JSON.\n\n\nRules:\n\n* Output must be ONLY JSON (no text before or after)\n* Do NOT skip any fields\n* If value is missing, return \"\"\n* All values must be strings\n* Dates must be in YYYY-MM-DD format\n* Status must be one of: New, In Production, Shipped, Delivered, Delayed, Follow-up Needed\n* Detect language: English or French\n* If Last_Update is not found, use today's date in the format\n{{ $now.format('yyyy-MM-dd') }}\n\nJSON format:\n{\n\"Order_ID\": \"string\",\n\"Client_Name\": \"string\",\n\"Supplier_Name\": \"string\",\n\"Status\": \"string\",\n\"Order_Date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\",\n\"Delivery_Date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\",\n\"Last_Update\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\",\n\"Source_Email\": \"string\",\n\"Language\": \"string\",\n\"Notes\": \"string\"\n}\n"
